SubjectOrder Fixing the Day on Which this Order is Made as the Day on Which Sections 1 and 4 and 14 to 18 of the Miscarriage of Justice Review Commission Act (David and Joyce Milgaard's law) Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing the day on which this Order is made as the day on which sections 1 and 4 and 14 to 18 of the MISCARRIAGE OF JUSTICE REVIEW COMMISSION ACT (DAVID AND JOYCE MILGAARD'S LAW) COME INTO FORCE in order to amend the Criminal Code by adding Part XXI.2 and make consequential amendments to other Acts.
